Base project containing all my settings for both Linux and MacOS systems.
On a freshly installed sytem, clone this repo to $HOME:

$ git clone git@github.com:elf-alchemist/dotfiles.git ~/dotfiles
$ cd ~/dotfiles

To get started, run the following, and Make will guide you on the rest:

$ make

And if you are on MacOS you shall install Homebrew as the following:

$ bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)"
$ make brew

Allowing you to install up-to-date packages.

